<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= titolo %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/chi-siamo">Chi Siamo</a>
        <a href="/progetto">Progetto</a>
        <a href="/storia">Storia</a>
        <a href="/dashboard" style="background: #4a90d9;">Dashboard Petoi</a>
    </nav>
    <main>
        <h1><%= titolo %></h1>
        <p class="subtitle"><%= sottotitolo %></p>
        <div class="content">
            <div style="overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <img src="/colombo.jpg" alt="Ritratto di Cristoforo Colombo" style="float: left; margin: 0 25px 15px 0; width: 280px; height: 280px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #1a4a6e; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
                <p>Cristoforo Colombo nacque a Genova intorno al 1451, in una famiglia di tessitori. Il padre Domenico era un cardatore di lana, e Cristoforo trascorse la sua giovinezza tra il laboratorio paterno e il porto, dove sviluppò una passione irresistibile per il mare e la navigazione. Ricevette un'educazione sommaria, ma imparò a leggere e scrivere, studiando con interesse le carte nautiche e i testi geografici dell'epoca.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <img src="/navigazione.jpg" alt="Cristoforo Colombo navigatore" style="float: right; margin: 0 0 15px 25px; width: 280px; height: 280px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #1a4a6e; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
                <p>Da giovane, Colombo navigò nel Mar Mediterraneo come marinaio e mercante, visitando porti come Genova, Lisbona e le isole dell'Atlantico. Si stabilì a Lisbona, dove sposò Filipa Moniz Perestrello, figlia di un nobile portoghese. Qui approfondì i suoi studi di cartografia e geografia, convincendosi sempre più che fosse possibile raggiungere le Indie navigando verso ovest. Leggendo opere come il "Libro di Marco Polo" e le carte del geografo Paolo Toscanelli, maturò l'idea di una nuova rotta commerciale verso l'Asia.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <img src="/recattolici.jpg" alt="Colombo davanti ai Re Cattolici" style="float: left; margin: 0 25px 15px 0; width: 280px; height: 280px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #1a4a6e; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
                <p>Per realizzare il suo sogno, Colombo cercò per anni un sovrano disposto a finanziare la spedizione. Nel 1485 presentò il suo progetto al Re del Portogallo Giovanni II, che lo rifiutò. Si rivolse allora ai Re Cattolici di Spagna, Ferdinando e Isabella, che inizialmente respinsero la proposta. Solo dopo lunghe trattative e l'intercessione del tesoriere reale Luis de Santangel, i sovrani spagnoli accettarono di sostenere l'impresa. Il 17 aprile 1492 furono firmate le Capitolazioni di Santa Fe, che assegnavano a Colombo i titoli di Ammiraglio del Mare Oceano e Viceré delle terre che avrebbe scoperto. Era pronto per salpare verso l'ignoto.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 style="color: #1a3a5c; text-align: center; margin: 40px 0 20px; font-weight: normal; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;">Galleria Storica</h2>
        
        <div class="gallery-container">
            <button class="gallery-btn prev" onclick="changeSlide(-1)">&#10094;</button>
            <div class="gallery-slides">
                <div class="gallery-slide">
                    <img src="/mappa3.jpg" alt="Mappa del mondo">
                    <div class="gallery-caption">Il mondo conosciuto nel XV secolo</div>
                    <button class="fullscreen-btn" onclick="openFullscreen(0)" title="Schermo intero">&#x26F6;</button>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-slide">
                    <img src="/scogli.jpg" alt="Scogli sul mare">
                    <div class="gallery-caption">Scogliere atlantiche - Le coste scoperte da Colombo</div>
                    <button class="fullscreen-btn" onclick="openFullscreen(1)" title="Schermo intero">&#x26F6;</button>
                </div>
                <div class="gallery-slide">
                    <img src="/indiani.jpg" alt="Accampamento indiani">
                    <div class="gallery-caption">Nativi americani - I popoli delle Americhe</div>
                    <button class="fullscreen-btn" onclick="openFullscreen(2)" title="Schermo intero">&#x26F6;</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="gallery-btn next" onclick="changeSlide(1)">&#10095;</button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="gallery-dots">
            <span class="dot" onclick="goToSlide(0)"></span>
            <span class="dot" onclick="goToSlide(1)"></span>
            <span class="dot" onclick="goToSlide(2)"></span>
        </div>
        
        <style>
            .gallery-container {
                position: relative;
                width: 100vw;
                left: 50%;
                right: 50%;
                margin-left: -50vw;
                margin-right: -50vw;
                overflow: hidden;
                background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0d1b2a 0%, #1a3a5c 50%, #0d1b2a 100%);
            }
            
            .gallery-slides {
                display: flex;
                transition: transform 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
                will-change: transform;
            }
            
            .gallery-slide {
                min-width: 100%;
                position: relative;
            }
            
            .gallery-slide img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100vh;
                object-fit: cover;
                display: block;
                animation: waveFloat 20s ease-in-out infinite;
            }
            
            @keyframes waveFloat {
                0%, 100% { 
                    transform: scale(1.05) translateY(0); 
                }
                50% { 
                    transform: scale(1.08) translateY(-20px); 
                }
            }
            
            .gallery-container::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                height: 200px;
                background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0d1b2a 0%, transparent 100%);
                z-index: 2;
                pointer-events: none;
            }
            
            .gallery-container::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                bottom: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                height: 250px;
                background: linear-gradient(to top, #0d1b2a 0%, transparent 100%);
                z-index: 2;
                pointer-events: none;
            }
            
            .gallery-caption {
                position: absolute;
                bottom: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(13, 27, 42, 0.95) 0%, rgba(26, 74, 110, 0.7) 50%, transparent 100%);
                color: white;
                padding: 60px 20px 30px;
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 1.3em;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
            }
            
            .gallery-btn {
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                transform: translateY(-50%);
                background: rgba(26, 74, 110, 0.6);
                color: white;
                border: none;
                padding: 25px 20px;
                font-size: 2em;
                cursor: pointer;
                transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
                z-index: 10;
                backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .gallery-btn:hover {
                background: rgba(13, 27, 42, 0.9);
                padding: 25px 30px;
            }
            
            .gallery-btn.prev {
                left: 0;
            }
            
            .gallery-btn.next {
                right: 0;
            }
            
            .gallery-dots {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 15px;
                margin: 30px 0;
            }
            
            .dot {
                width: 16px;
                height: 16px;
                background: #a8c4d8;
                border-radius: 50%;
                cursor: pointer;
                transition: all 0.3s;
            }
            
            .dot.active {
                background: #1a4a6e;
                transform: scale(1.3);
            }
            
            .fullscreen-btn {
                position: absolute;
                top: 20px;
                right: 20px;
                background: rgba(26, 74, 110, 0.85);
                color: white;
                border: none;
                padding: 12px 16px;
                font-size: 1.5em;
                cursor: pointer;
                border-radius: 8px;
                transition: all 0.3s;
                z-index: 15;
            }
            
            .fullscreen-btn:hover {
                background: rgba(13, 32, 53, 0.95);
                transform: scale(1.1);
            }
        </style>
        
        <script>
            let currentSlide = 0;
            const totalSlides = 3;
            
            function changeSlide(n) {
                currentSlide += n;
                if (currentSlide >= totalSlides) currentSlide = 0;
                if (currentSlide < 0) currentSlide = totalSlides - 1;
                updateGallery();
            }
            
            function goToSlide(n) {
                currentSlide = n;
                updateGallery();
            }
            
            let scogliMessageTimeout = null;
            let scogliMessageElement = null;
            
            function updateGallery() {
                const slides = document.querySelector('.gallery-slides');
                slides.style.transform = `translateX(-${currentSlide * 100}%)`;
                
                const dots = document.querySelectorAll('.dot');
                dots.forEach((dot, index) => {
                    dot.classList.toggle('active', index === currentSlide);
                });
                
                if (scogliMessageTimeout) {
                    clearTimeout(scogliMessageTimeout);
                    scogliMessageTimeout = null;
                }
                
                if (scogliMessageElement) {
                    scogliMessageElement.remove();
                    scogliMessageElement = null;
                }
                
                if (currentSlide === 1) {
                    scogliMessageElement = document.createElement('div');
                    scogliMessageElement.style.cssText = `
                        position: fixed;
                        top: 50%;
                        left: 50%;
                        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
                        color: white;
                        font-size: 1.8em;
                        font-weight: bold;
                        text-align: center;
                        padding: 30px 50px;
                        z-index: 100;
                        text-shadow: 
                            -3px -3px 0 #000,
                            3px -3px 0 #000,
                            -3px 3px 0 #000,
                            3px 3px 0 #000,
                            -3px 0 0 #000,
                            3px 0 0 #000,
                            0 -3px 0 #000,
                            0 3px 0 #000,
                            0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
                        animation: fadeInMessage 0.5s ease-out;
                        pointer-events: none;
                    `;
                    scogliMessageElement.textContent = 'Oh no, gli scogli! Forse è meglio girare da questa parte per arrivare alle Indie';
                    document.body.appendChild(scogliMessageElement);
                    
                    scogliMessageTimeout = setTimeout(() => {
                        if (scogliMessageElement) {
                            scogliMessageElement.style.animation = 'fadeOutMessage 0.5s ease-out';
                            setTimeout(() => {
                                if (scogliMessageElement) {
                                    scogliMessageElement.remove();
                                    scogliMessageElement = null;
                                }
                            }, 500);
                        }
                    }, 5000);
                }
            }
            
            function openFullscreen(slideIndex) {
                const images = ['/mappa3.jpg', '/scogli.jpg', '/indiani.jpg'];
                let currentIndex = slideIndex;
                
                const overlay = document.createElement('div');
                overlay.style.cssText = `
                    position: fixed;
                    top: 0;
                    left: 0;
                    width: 100%;
                    height: 100%;
                    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
                    z-index: 10000;
                    display: flex;
                    align-items: center;
                    justify-content: center;
                `;
                
                const img = new Image();
                img.src = images[currentIndex];
                img.style.cssText = 'width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;';
                img.id = 'fullscreen-img';
                
                const closeBtn = document.createElement('button');
                closeBtn.innerHTML = '&times;';
                closeBtn.style.cssText = `
                    position: absolute;
                    top: 20px;
                    right: 30px;
                    background: rgba(26, 74, 110, 0.9);
                    color: white;
                    border: none;
                    width: 50px;
                    height: 50px;
                    font-size: 2em;
                    cursor: pointer;
                    border-radius: 50%;
                    z-index: 10001;
                `;
                closeBtn.onclick = () => overlay.remove();
                
                const prevBtn = document.createElement('button');
                prevBtn.innerHTML = '&#10094;';
                prevBtn.style.cssText = `
                    position: absolute;
                    left: 20px;
                    top: 50%;
                    transform: translateY(-50%);
                    background: rgba(26, 74, 110, 0.8);
                    color: white;
                    border: none;
                    padding: 20px 15px;
                    font-size: 2em;
                    cursor: pointer;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    z-index: 10001;
                    transition: all 0.3s;
                `;
                prevBtn.onmouseover = () => prevBtn.style.background = 'rgba(13, 27, 42, 0.9)';
                prevBtn.onmouseout = () => prevBtn.style.background = 'rgba(26, 74, 110, 0.8)';
                prevBtn.onclick = (e) => {
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    currentIndex = (currentIndex - 1 + images.length) % images.length;
                    img.src = images[currentIndex];
                };
                
                const nextBtn = document.createElement('button');
                nextBtn.innerHTML = '&#10095;';
                nextBtn.style.cssText = `
                    position: absolute;
                    right: 20px;
                    top: 50%;
                    transform: translateY(-50%);
                    background: rgba(26, 74, 110, 0.8);
                    color: white;
                    border: none;
                    padding: 20px 15px;
                    font-size: 2em;
                    cursor: pointer;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    z-index: 10001;
                    transition: all 0.3s;
                `;
                nextBtn.onmouseover = () => nextBtn.style.background = 'rgba(13, 27, 42, 0.9)';
                nextBtn.onmouseout = () => nextBtn.style.background = 'rgba(26, 74, 110, 0.8)';
                nextBtn.onclick = (e) => {
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % images.length;
                    img.src = images[currentIndex];
                };
                
                overlay.appendChild(img);
                overlay.appendChild(closeBtn);
                overlay.appendChild(prevBtn);
                overlay.appendChild(nextBtn);
                overlay.onclick = (e) => {
                    if (e.target === overlay) overlay.remove();
                };
                
                document.addEventListener('keydown', function handleKeydown(e) {
                    if (e.key === 'ArrowLeft') {
                        currentIndex = (currentIndex - 1 + images.length) % images.length;
                        img.src = images[currentIndex];
                    } else if (e.key === 'ArrowRight') {
                        currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % images.length;
                        img.src = images[currentIndex];
                    } else if (e.key === 'Escape') {
                        overlay.remove();
                        document.removeEventListener('keydown', handleKeydown);
                    }
                });
                
                document.body.appendChild(overlay);
            }
            
            function showNotification(message) {
                const notification = document.createElement('div');
                notification.style.cssText = `
                    position: fixed;
                    top: 20px;
                    right: 20px;
                    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a4a6e, #0d1b2a);
                    color: white;
                    padding: 20px 30px;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
                    z-index: 9999;
                    animation: slideIn 0.5s ease;
                `;
                notification.textContent = message;
                document.body.appendChild(notification);
                
                setTimeout(() => {
                    notification.style.animation = 'slideOut 0.5s ease';
                    setTimeout(() => notification.remove(), 500);
                }, 3000);
            }
            
            const eventSource = new EventSource('/events');
            
            eventSource.onmessage = (event) => {
                const data = JSON.parse(event.data);
                
                if (data.type === 'gallery-next') {
                    changeSlide(1);
                    showNotification(`Petoi ha visto: ${data.reason}`);
                }
                
                if (data.type === 'object-detected') {
                    console.log(`Oggetto rilevato: ${data.object}`);
                }
            };
            
            eventSource.onerror = () => {
                console.log('Riconnessione in corso...');
            };
            
            updateGallery();
        </script>
        <style>
            @keyframes slideIn {
                from { transform: translateX(400px); opacity: 0; }
                to { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 1; }
            }
            @keyframes slideOut {
                from { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 1; }
                to { transform: translateX(400px); opacity: 0; }
            }
            @keyframes fadeInMessage {
                from { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.9); }
                to { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
            }
            @keyframes fadeOutMessage {
                from { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); }
                to { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0.9); }
            }
        </style>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>Colombo App 2026</p>
    </footer>
    <script src="/js/rocks.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/sunset.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/ships.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
